*       Ё                                                         Ё
*       Ё _5450HTTOH           m.nombre VALID                     Ё
*       Ё                                                         Ё
*       Ё Function Origin:                                        Ё
*       Ё                                                         Ё
*       Ё From Platform:       MS-DOS                             Ё
*       Ё From Screen:         RUBROS2,     Record Number:    6   Ё
*       Ё Variable:            m.nombre                           Ё
*       Ё Called By:           VALID Clause                       Ё
*       Ё Object Type:         Field                              Ё
